claim.claim-text:
1. An image pickup device provided with an automatic focusing function, comprising:
an image pickup unit configured to input image data corresponding to a subject;
a face detection unit configured to separately detect eyes, a nose, and a mouth of a human face from the image data input from the image pickup unit;
a ranging area selection unit, by which when the eyes, the nose, and the mouth are separately detected by the face detection unit, a user selects any one of the eyes, the nose, or the mouth as a ranging area; and
an automatic focusing control unit configured to perform automatic focusing control based on the ranging area selected by the ranging area selection unit.

11. An automatic focusing method comprising:
inputting image data corresponding to a subject;
separately detecting eyes, a nose, and a mouth of a human face from the image data input at the image input step;
providing a plurality of markers on a screen, one of the plurality of markers corresponding to each of the eyes, the nose, and the mouth;
receiving from a user a selection of any one of the plurality of markers corresponding to the eyes, the nose, or the mouth as a ranging area; and
performing automatic focusing control based on the ranging area selected by the user.

12. A program configured to be stored on a computer readable medium and when executed by a computer, the program configured to perform an automatic focusing method, comprising:
separately detecting eyes, a nose, and a mouth of a human face from the image data input at the image input step;
providing a plurality of markers on a screen, one of the plurality of markers corresponding to each of the eyes, the nose, and the mouth;
receiving from a user a selection of any one of the plurality of markers corresponding to the eyes, the nose, or the mouth as a ranging area; and
performing automatic focusing control based on the ranging area selected by the user.
